                        <div id="ctl00_description" class="summary">This article focuses on how to listen for signals from an Arduino through the Serial Port (Linux, Mac) or COM Port for Windows using the SerialPort2 Node.JS module and serve signal data to the web in real time using Socket.IO.</div>			

                    </div>
                    
					
					

					

					
					
					

						
					

					

						
